sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Alpine as Alpine.js<br/>(client state)
    participant HTMX
    participant Django
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    %% ── Initial page load ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    User->>Django: GET /flows/history/
    Django->>DB: SELECT FlowExecution (unfiltered, default sort)
    DB-->>Django: queryset
    Note over Django: Builds table_config<br/>(active_filters=[], sort="-created_at")<br/>Paginates results
    Django-->>User: Full page HTML<br/>(table.html with Alpine root)
    Note over Alpine: Init:<br/>• Load hiddenCols from localStorage<br/>• filterRows = [] (no active filters)<br/>• selectedIds = new Set()

    %% ── User opens filter panel and adds a filter ─────────────────────────────
    User->>Alpine: clicks "Filters ▾"
    Alpine-->>User: filtersOpen = true (dropdown visible)

    User->>Alpine: clicks "Add filter"
    Alpine-->>User: appends {field:'',op:'',value:''} to filterRows<br/>→ new filter row rendered

    User->>Alpine: selects field="status", op="eq", value="COMPLETED"
    Alpine-->>User: filterRows[0] updated (no server call yet)

    User->>Alpine: clicks "Apply"
    Note over Alpine: Builds URL:<br/>/flows/history/?f_field[]=status&f_op[]=eq<br/>&f_val[]=COMPLETED&sort=-created_at&page=1
    Alpine->>HTMX: htmx.ajax('GET', url, {target:'#dt-history-body', pushUrl: url})

    HTMX->>Django: GET /flows/history/?f_field[]=status&f_op[]=eq&f_val[]=COMPLETED<br/>HX-Request: true
    Django->>DB: SELECT … WHERE status='COMPLETED' ORDER BY -created_at
    DB-->>Django: filtered queryset
    Note over Django: Rebuilds active_filters=[{field:'status',op:'eq',value:'COMPLETED'}]<br/>Paginates
    Django-->>HTMX: Partial HTML (tbody rows + pagination + active chips)
    HTMX-->>User: Swaps #dt-history-body, pushes URL to browser history
    Note over Alpine: filtersOpen = false<br/>(closed by applyFilters())

    %% ── User dismisses one filter chip ───────────────────────────────────────
    User->>Alpine: clicks ✕ on "status = COMPLETED" chip
    Note over Alpine: Removes filter from filterRows,<br/>calls applyFilters() with remaining filters
    Alpine->>HTMX: htmx.ajax('GET', /flows/history/?sort=-created_at&page=1, ...)
    HTMX->>Django: GET /flows/history/ (no filter params)
    Django->>DB: SELECT … (unfiltered)
    DB-->>Django: full queryset
    Django-->>HTMX: Partial HTML (unfiltered table)
    HTMX-->>User: Table updated, URL updated to /flows/history/

    %% ── User clicks a sortable column header ─────────────────────────────────
    User->>Alpine: clicks "Status ↕" column header
    Note over Alpine: Toggles sort: "" → "status" → "-status" → ""<br/>Calls htmx.ajax with &sort=status
    HTMX->>Django: GET /flows/history/?sort=status (+ any active filters)
    Django->>DB: SELECT … ORDER BY status ASC
    DB-->>Django: sorted queryset
    Django-->>HTMX: Partial HTML
    HTMX-->>User: Table updated, sort arrow changes to ↑
